_sText:
I've been working on this map in conjunction with my friend Vincent. This is a very rough version of what we'd like it to be. I'd like to hear any criticism that you may be able to provide. Thanks for checking it out and I hope you like it.

*Update*1.1 So I've added the garage that I mentioned in the video, changed a few textures, cleaned up some lines in the house, and moved the trees around a bit. Expect the front gate, driveway, and depending on how it looks a fountain in the next few days.
